Source:
  Title: The Complete Works of Chuang Tzu
  ID: 50ae0a98-5702-40cb-8c11-4c6297aa457a
  Translator: Burton Watson
By: Zhuangzi
Locus:
  Chapter: 12
  Paragraph: 13
Title: Heaven And Earth
---
Yao was seeing the sights at Hua when the border guard of Hua said,
"Aha - a sage! I beg to offer up prayers for the sage. They will bring
the sage long life!"
